<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,654,1039]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,304,654,679]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487">Distribution.</emphasis>
Widely distributed in the north and south Atlantic, Pacific and Indian Oceans, also 
<collectingRegion box="[1306,1384,654,679]" country="United States of America" name="Alaska" pageId="6" pageNumber="487">Alaska</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[151,271,690,715]" name="Antarctica" pageId="6" pageNumber="487">Antarctica</collectingCountry>
