<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,654,1039]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,978,1003]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487">Remarks.</emphasis>
Due to the presence of this species in Italy (
<bibRefCitation author="Vives" box="[806,936,978,1003]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487" refString="Vives, F. (1968) Sur les Malacostraces planctoniques des mers Tyrrhenienne et Catalane. Rapports et Proces-Verbaux des Reunions (International Commission for the Scientific Exploration of the Mediterranean Sea), 19 (3), 459 - 461." type="journal article" year="1968">Vives 1968</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmann" box="[948,1230,978,1003]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487" refString="Wittmann, K. J. &amp; Ariani, A. P. (2010) Lophogastrida &amp; Mysida. Biologia Marina Mediterranea, 17 (1), 474 - 483." type="journal article" year="2010">Wittmann &amp; Ariani,2010</bibRefCitation>
) we suspect that it is likely be found in the Iberian Mediterranean Sea.
</paragraph>
